  "short_description": "\"Dust & Courage: Jake Bolton's Journey\" is an open-world, single-player RPG set in a fantasy Wild West. You play as cowboy Jake Bolton; every choice is yours. Talk or fight, pick friends or foes, explore towns and deserts, and shape your own adventure. Your adventure, your rules.",
